\id 1TH - Waunan (Woun Meu) NT (alternate orthography) -Colombia 2011 (DBL -2013) 
\h 1 TESALONICENSES 
\toc1 Nacharam ẽsap Pabloou Tesalónicapienag phã deepʉ̈itarr 
\toc2 1 Tesalonicenses 
\toc3 1 Te 
\mt1 1 TESALONICENSES 
\mt2 Nacharam ẽsap Pabloou Tesalónicapienag phã deepʉ̈itarr 
\ip \bd Chi phãtarr\bd*. Mʉg carta Pabloouta phãjim. Irua carta phãmatarr khapan thʉnʉm ee chamʉg nacharam carta Tesalónicapienag deepʉ̈itarrta tagam khãaijã nacha phãjimjöo sim. 
\ip \bd Chijã khʉʉn atheeta phãjĩ.\bd* Pabloou Tesalónicapienag maach peerdʉajem iek jawaan maawai irua jaau nʉrrʉm khõchkhabam khʉʉn pöoma thʉnaajim aajem (Hch. 17:1-9). Tesalónicapien ʉ̈rcha judionaan khabam khʉʉn ajieb mamʉ, Pabloou jaau nʉrrʉm ũrwi ʉ̈u khapanaam khʉʉnauta ʉ̈khajierram aajem. Mamʉ ĩchab ãaur khʉʉn judionaan aig narr khʉʉnau mag Pabloou jajaaukham ũrwi amach eem khʉʉnaupa jũrram khʉʉnau ʉ̈khaphö thʉnʉm oobaawai, warag Pablo dʉ̈ita meeurrkha phöbaadëwi warre amach phöbör eemua jʉrpʉ̈ijierram anaabá. Maimua mawia Corinto barbaimaawai jũrr Timoteo Tesalonicaag pʉ̈ijim aajem, mam chi ʉ̈kha durrarr khʉʉndam wawimamua am khĩir onee apimkhĩir. Irua khaphʉ sĩejim, mamaam khʉʉn dʉ̈i chi ʉ̈khaba nʉm khʉʉn garmua khaigba nʉm (2:14; 3:1-5). Maimua Timoteo bëewi ʉ̈u amachdëu ʉ̈khatarr iek gaai agtha ubʉ nʉm a jaaubaicheewaita Pablo oneeubaadëwi mʉg nacharam carta amag deepʉ̈ijim aajem, ich mag amach narrjö ogdʉba wënʉrrapi jaaupäaig (3:6-7). 
\ip \bd Khan jawaag ajĩ.\bd* Mʉg ẽsap gaaipai am khĩir onee iekhanaa, am kha khõsi simjã jaaunaa, warag nem khĩir pogkhe jaaumamua am wawí sim, jãga naaju aai nʉ a khap amkhĩir (4:1-12; 5:12-22). Deeu Cristo bëeju anʉm amau khĩirju nʉmjã Pabloou khaphʉ sĩejim. Amau ajapha khaphʉ am khõsi naajim aajem, jãga aju Ẽwandamau Cristo iek ʉ̈kha nʉm ee mee nʉm khʉʉn dʉ̈i. Amau mag khap am khõsi narr aawai jöoi Pabloou ajaphata mag deeu Cristo bëeju anʉmjã amag jaaupʉ̈ijim (5:1-11). Ich mag capítulo ö nʉmpierr jöoirau ich ag iekpaita phʉrëu jajawagmam (1:10; 2:19-20; 3:13; 4:13-18; 5:23). 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Mʉch Pabloouta Silvano dʉ̈i Timoteopa ãba nʉmua mʉg ẽsap phã deepʉ̈i chirʉm pãar Tesalónica phöbör ee Cristo gaaimua maach ãba khodkha nʉm khʉʉnag. Mua khaphʉ chirʉm, chadcha pãar Ẽwandam chi Aai gaai ubʉ thierrkhanaa ĩchab maach Pör Jesucristo dʉ̈ijã ubʉ nʉm. Marau Ẽwandamagta jëeu nʉm, pãar ʉ̈uu wai sĩenaa ĩchab khõinaa wai sĩemkhĩir. 
\s1 Jãga wënʉrrajĩ Tesalónicapien õor dau na 
\p  
\v 2 Maran mau warp naab mamʉ, ed ëepierr maachdëu Ẽwandamag jëeuwai irigta ʉ̈u ajim a durraajem pãar kõit.  
\v 3 Mag pãar igwia irig ʉ̈u ajim anʉm aig ĩchab marau khĩir eyaa aajem, jãga pãrau pãachdëu ʉ̈khatarr iek gaai bʉ̈ʉrjã iekchëba warag phidkham khõsi phidkha nʉ, maimua jãga mag maach Pör Jesucristo bëejujã khõsi nʉ nʉm gaaimua chikhamnau pãach dʉ̈i khaigba aadëp aawaijã ichdëu pãar eeg oojẽ, magʉm iekjã igba ãwat wënʉrramkhĩir. Marau khaphʉ nʉm, pãrau chadcha dich khapeen kha khõsinaa Ẽwandamjã khõsi naawaita jãg phidkha nʉm. Mag gaaimuata irig ʉ̈u ajim a durraajem pãar kõit.  
\v 4 Cristo gaaimua khodamnaan, marau khaphʉ nʉm chadcha ich Ẽwandamauta pãar jʉr aujim. Magtarr aawai ichdëujã chadcha pãar khõsi sim.  
\v 5 Marau pãar aar Ẽwandam iek jaau wënʉrraawai sĩi maachdëu jaaum khõchgaupai khaba, ich Ẽwandam Akhaar ag jua theegau jaaupibaawai ajim; maimua mag nʉm dʉ̈i ĩchab chadcharam iekkha sim maachdëujã khaphʉ nʉisiewai ajim. Pãrau khaphʉ nʉm, jãga pãar ee maar wënʉrrajĩ, pãach ʉ̈u wajapha wënʉrramkhĩir. 
\p  
\v 6 Pãach daúa maar mag wajapha wënʉrrʉm oobaawai, pãrau maar wënʉrraajemjö awia ĩchab maach Pör Jesús nʉrrarrjö ajierram. Ich ag gaaimua pãar phithurg aujierrab mamʉ, ich Ẽwandam Akharauta pãar thãar onee api sĩewai pãrau maach peerdʉajem iekjã onee ʉ̈khajierram.  
\v 7 Pãachdëu magtarr gaaimua Macedoniapienau maimua Acayapienaujã thum chi ʉ̈kha durrarr khʉʉnau ʉ̈u pãar agpierraa wënʉrrʉm oo nʉm.  
\v 8 Pãar aigmuata maach Pör Jesucristo iekhan sĩi aaidʉbaadëm. Mag aaidʉbaadëm sĩi Macedonia durrpaijã khaba, ni Acaya durrpaijã khaba, durrpierrta aaidʉ jöisim. Mag nʉm dʉ̈i ĩchab pãachdëu Ẽwandam iek ʉ̈khatarrpai ogdʉba ʉ̈kha nʉmjã thumaam khʉʉnau khakhapdö thʉnʉm. Mag khakhapdö wëjöm aawai marau tag pãar jaauju aai khaba nʉm.  
\v 9 Marau amachig jaauju nawe amach garmuata marag jaau nʉm, marau pãar oon weetwai jãga pãrau maar pãach ee baarpijĩ, maimua jãga parhoobam nemta pãach ẽwandamkha wai nʉnʉid arrjã isegmajierrá, jũrr Ẽwandam chaar chadcha iiu sĩejemʉgpaita jëeu wënʉrraag.  
\v 10 Ẽwandam Iewaa Jesús meewia iiu phiidʉtarr ʉ̈gtharmua deeu bëeju pãrau nʉ nʉmjã mau marag jaau nʉm ĩchab. Magua maach Pör Jesuugta ʉ̈u ajim a chirʉm, ʉ̈u i gaaimuata Ẽwandamau maach i agkham ed maach gaai jua khʉaba deeju arrjã maach peerdʉ autarr aawai. 
\c 2  
\s1 Pablo phidag Tesalónica phöbör ee 
\p  
\v 1 Khodamnaan, pãrau khaphʉ nʉm, maar pãar aar udthuurwai ʉ̈u parcha khabajim.  
\v 2 Pãrau khaphʉ nʉm ĩchab, Filipos phöbör ee naawai õrau maach khĩirchajã iekhanaa maar dʉ̈i khaigba aajerr; mamʉ mag nʉm ãba ʉ̈u Ẽwandamau maar eeg oowi maar juagjã oojim, mʉg iek phithurg aadëphʉm eejã ogdʉba warag ichdëu maach peerdʉ aaujem iekta pãrag jaaumkhĩir.  
\v 3 Marau maachdëu jaau wënʉrrarr iek wajapha khaphʉ narr aawai, imeerkhawi sëukhajã nem jaauba, ni juau ogthom chikham khũguraagpaijã khaba chadchata jaau wënʉrrajim,  
\v 4 ich Ẽwandamauta maar jʉr auwia ichdëu õor peerdʉ aaujem iekta jaaupitarr aawai. Maguata marau mʉg i iek jaau wënʉrrʉm. Mag jaau wënʉrrʉm chan mag sĩi õrag maach khõigpim khõchgaujã khaba, ich Ẽwandamau ichdëuta maach thãarjã khogreu jʉrmamjö thum khaphʉ sĩerrʉmua oowaijã magta ʉ̈u sĩewaita mag jaau wënʉrrʉm.  
\v 5 Pãrau khaphʉ nʉm ĩchab, marau sĩi maachdëu jaau wënʉrrʉm iek ʉ̈khamkhĩirjã chadam iekjö pãar thö iekhaba, ni sĩi mag wënʉrrʉmua phatkhon aum khõchgaujã khabata mag jaaujeejim. Marau mag jaau wënʉrraajerr Ẽwandamaujã khaphʉ sim.  
\v 6 Marau mag sĩi õrau maachigta ee amkhĩirjã jʉrba, ni pãragjã maach igwia maarta thö iyʉ̈ʉ abatjã abajim.  
\v 7 Cristoou ich i jaaumkhĩir maachta jʉr autarr aawai chadcha iek theeg nʉm awia marau pãar dʉ̈i maachdëu am aig aju aai naajim. Mamʉ magjã magba sĩi warag chaain daumeraamjö naajim pãar ee. Pãrau ooba aajẽ, jãga ʉʉirau bʉ̈ʉrjã ich chaain chig aba jãsene phë wai sĩejẽ.  
\v 8 Ich jãgta pãarjã marau daupii wai naabajieb; magua marau pãrag Ẽwandam iek jaaum khõchag naajim. Pari mag jaau nʉmpaijã khaba, ag gaaimua pãar kõit maar khëchju arr akhiinjã ya nawe khëchwia naakham, pãar daupigau.  
\v 9 Khodamnaan, pãrau khĩir eyaa nʉm, maar pãar ee udthuurwai jãga maar khajeeu durrum ãba phidkhaajeejĩ maach bidam athee. Ẽwandamau maach peerdʉ aaujem iek pãrag jaau wënʉrrʉmua edaram magwe maar phidkhaajeejim, eeu naspawia ãbmua khãijã maar jãogam khõchgau ichta khöjudamjã chukkhu chirajim am ugua. \fig |src="CN01997B.TIF" size="col" copy="© 1978 David C. Cook Publishing Co." ref="1TH 2.9" \fig* 
\p  
\v 10 Pãrau khaphʉ nʉm, Ẽwandam dau na maar bʉ̈ʉrjã khaigba khaba khajaphata wënʉrraajeejim. Magua pãar eem khʉʉnau ni ãbmuajã bʉ̈ʉrjã marag magʉm aba aajeejim. Maagjerr pãrau pãach daúa oowia ĩchab ich Ẽwandamaujã khaphʉ sim.  
\v 11 Khĩir eyaa abat ĩchab, chi ayau ich chaain wawiejemjö marau pãach wawinaa pãach khĩir jãsenkhaajerr.  
\v 12 Mag wawimamua marau pãrag “Chadcha Ẽwandam dau na wënʉrraju aai nʉmjöta wënʉrrathʉ̈” aajeejim, ichdëu durr jʉ̈a sim gaai wënʉrramkhĩir ichdëuta maach thʉ̈r sĩewai. 
\p  
\v 13 Maguata maraun ich jãg Ẽwandamag ʉ̈u ajim a durraajem. Marau Ẽwandam iek jaau wënʉrrarr pãrau ũurwai chadcha Ẽwandam iek aawaita pãrau ʉ̈khajierram. Jã chan sĩi khajap maach iekpaijã khabajim; jãan Ẽwandam iekhau. Magtarr aawai ichdëuta pãar wajaug paa arrum.  
\v 14 Khodamnaan, ar pãach durr eepai ãba naajem khʉʉnaupai pãar khaibag wawaag athee pãar ẽudee ẽkha naawai, Judea durrjã agjö Ẽwandam iek ʉ̈kha durrum khʉʉn dʉ̈i arrjöta ajierram pãar dʉ̈ijã. Amjã pãarjö Jesucristo dën aawai pãar dʉ̈i arrjö amach durram khʉʉnaupaita am ẽudee ẽkhaajeejim.  
\v 15 Ich makhʉʉn judionaanauta maach Pör Jesús thõopʉ̈ijierram, warrgarwe maach jöoin Ẽwandam i jaau durraajerr khʉʉn kheechjerrjö. Mag i thõopʉ̈iwia maarjã khaibag wawaag ẽkha nʉmua warag maar deeum durrag jʉr wërppʉ̈ijierram. Jãkhʉʉnau chan Ẽwandam dau na bʉ̈ʉrjã nem wajapham wauba aajem. Amach mag nʉm gaaimua ni iwiir ãbam khʉʉnaujã Ẽwandam iek jaau nʉm igar khaba nʉm.  
\v 16 Maguata judionaan khabam khʉʉnagpa maach peerdʉajem iek jaaum iigwaijã magjã khõchkhaba nʉm. Amach mag nʉm gaaimua amachta warag Ẽwandam dʉ̈i iekkhõr pöoma naawai Ẽwandamau am gaai mas deeb khaba deeju. 
\s1 Pabloou deeu Tesalónicapien oon mam khõchag sĩerr 
\p  
\v 17 Khodamnaan, pãar aig naawia ërëu phöbaadeeu tag marau pãar oobaa nʉisijim. Mamʉ magʉm ãba, marau ʉ̈iba pãar iigjeejim. Maguata pãar oon mam khõchaaga naajim.  
\v 18 Mag naawai wëtju ẽkhajim; mʉchchajã maju ẽkhajim. Mamʉ dösãtau idëu mʉ mapibajim.  
\v 19 Pãadë khĩirjubat: ¿Chijã khʉʉnta marau iigjem abarí? ¿Chijã khʉʉn gaaimuata maar oneenaa mʉg atagjã Ẽwandamau nem wajapham deebarm auju khĩirju nʉm khai? Pãar gaaimuama; pãarta marau iigjem. Maach Pör Jesucristo bëem edjã pãar gaaimuata maar onee aju.  
\v 20 Pãar gaaimuata maar oneenaa mʉg atagjã maar ʉ̈ucha nʉisiju. 
\c 3  
\p  
\v 1 Mag pãar jãga nʉ a khap am khõchag chirʉmjã pöd maba aawai Atenas phöbör ee mʉch appai thʉbawi  
\v 2 jũrr maach khodam Timoteota mua pʉ̈ijim, ĩchab Cristo iek jawaag Ẽwandamau ichig nem mag aawai bʉ̈ʉrjã i ichaaur magʉm aba khitaawai. Iita mua pʉ̈ijim, pãar oon mawia pãachdëu ʉ̈kha nʉm iek gaai ubʉ naamkhĩir warag pãrag jaaumkhĩir,  
\v 3 maagwai jãg phithurg aadëphʉm gaaimuajã ni iwiir ãbjã deeu ewag mam ugua. Pãrau khaphʉ nʉm, maachin ich jãgta Ẽwandamau ich gaaimua phithurg ãwat wënʉrrapim khõsi sim.  
\v 4 Maach ipaarmua nawejã marau pãrag, ichiita maachin ich jãg õrau maach dʉ̈i khaigba nʉm gaaimua ökhĩirjugjã ãwatab khaba ãwat wënʉrraju a jaau naajim. Magtarr aawai chadcha ag ee öbërjim. Majã pãrau khaphʉ nʉm.  
\v 5 Mag pãar jãga nʉ a khap am khõchag chirʉm tag mʉchdëu ãwatba aadeewaita mua Timoteo pʉ̈ijim, jãga pãrau Ẽwandam iek pãachdëu ʉ̈khatarr ee wënʉrrʉ́ a khap jëeumkhĩir. Mua pãar khĩirju chirajim, eeu dëgölp dösãtau khãijã pãrag nem khaigba waupibarm gaaimua deeu khãijã ewag ërëu phöbaadeewai sĩi parta maach phidkhabarmjö aju khĩirjuwia. 
\p  
\v 6 Mamʉ ya ʉ̈u deeu Timoteo Tesalónicamua barbaichëm, pãar oothurwia. I iek mag pãar Ẽwandam iek gaai ubʉnaa pãach khapeenjã agdaujö khõsi nʉm aajem. I iek mag ĩchab pãach garmuajã maar khĩir eyaanaa maar oom khõchag naajem aajem, ich jãg maraujã pãar oom khõchag naajemjö.  
\v 7 Khodamnaan, maguata mʉg phithurg aadëphʉm dʉ̈i gaai machagjã aadëp ab mamʉ, maar dʉ̈rrcha onee naajem, pãrau pãachdëu ʉ̈khatarr iek gaai ogdʉba agtha pëdurraawai.  
\v 8 Mag maach Pör Jesucristo dʉ̈ita pãar ubʉ nʉm a ũurwaita maachpajã warag khĩirdam ubʉ aphöbaadeejem.  
\v 9 Jãga akhiin mʉg pãar gaaimua Ẽwandam na maach onee nʉm paar agpierr irig ʉ̈u ajim abpʉ̈ikham.  
\v 10 Edaram magwe Ẽwandamag jëeu durrumua deeu ũwaai pãar dʉ̈i khĩircha oobarkhiina a durraajem, mag ãba nʉisiewai agtha pãrau khaugba nʉmdam jaaubarmua khaugbaawai warag ubʉ nʉisimkhĩir. 
\p  
\v 11 Ẽwandam maach Ayau maach Pör Jesús dʉ̈imua maar pʉ̈ikhiin ʉ̈u akham a durraajem, pãar oon wëtaag.  
\v 12 Mag dʉ̈i ĩchab maach Pör Jesuugjã pãar kõit jëeu nʉm, ich jãg maachdëujã pãar khõsi nʉmjö pãarjã warag agdaujö thumaa jũrr chikham kha khõsi apimkhĩir.  
\v 13 Ichdëuta pãar thãarjã ãba ichigta khĩirjupinaa bʉ̈ʉrjã pekau chukhu wai sĩepim khõsi nʉm maach Aai Ẽwandam na, deeu ũwaai thum ich igar ʉ̈kha thʉnʉm khʉʉn dʉ̈i bëe nʉm ora. Ich mag maachdëu jëeu nʉmjö akhiin ʉ̈u akham keena. 
\c 4  
\s1 Ẽwandam oowai ʉ̈uum nem 
\p  
\v 1 Khodamnaan, maach Pör Jesús iekta maach iek gaai thʉwi ĩs marau pãrag magam ig nʉm: Ich jãg maachdëu pãachig jaautarrjö, Ẽwandamag pãach ʉ̈uu oomkhĩir, ar pãach nʉmjö ich jãg agpierraata wënʉrrathʉ̈. 
\p  
\v 2 Maach Pör Jesuu pãrag jaaupibaawai marau pãachig jaautarr ya pãrau khaphʉ nʉm.  
\v 3 Ẽwandamaun ãba ich atheepaita maachig nem wau wënʉrrapim khõsi sim; ni iwiir ãbjã dich õor khabam dʉ̈i khapese aba.  
\v 4 Magju khãai sĩi agdaujö dich ʉʉi chaar aunaa, i dʉ̈i agpierraanaa, aairaa aju aai nʉm, i dʉ̈i dichdëu ampierr aba;  
\v 5 mag dich ʉʉi dʉ̈i pawiajã, sĩi õor Ẽwandam khaugbam khʉʉnjö i dʉ̈i khĩir lököo khaba, sĩi i dʉ̈i khapes ajupaijã khĩirjuba.  
\v 6 Ni ãbmuajã oob dich khapeen ʉʉin wau sĩsid amiet, ni magʉm gaaimuajã pãach khapeen khũgurmiet. Na maachdëu pãach khĩircha jaau narrjö, magʉm paran Ẽwandamaujã jua khʉaba deejem, ichdëujã jãg khõchkhaba sĩerraawai.  
\v 7 Ẽwandamau maach ich athee jʉr autarr chan sĩi parhooba pekau wau wënʉrramkhĩir khabajim. Magju khãai ichdëu khõsi simjö ich athee nem wajapha wau nʉmpai wau wënʉrramkhĩirta maach ich dënkha aujim.  
\v 8 Magtarr aawai chamʉg nem wajapha wau nʉmta iseg sim wounaun chi jaau wënʉrrʉm khʉʉnta isegba, ich Ẽwandam ichdëu maachig ich Akhaar deejemchata iseg sim, chamʉg maachdëu jaau wënʉrrʉm iekjã i dën aawai. 
\p  
\v 9 Mʉg Ẽwandam iek ʉ̈kha nʉm gaaimua khodkha thʉnʉm khʉʉn aphajã warag chikham kha khõsi amkhĩir chan mua tag pãrag bʉ̈ʉrjã jaaupʉ̈ibam, ich Ẽwandamauchata ya pãar mag khõsi wënʉrraa khaugpi sĩewai.  
\v 10 Macedonia durram khʉʉn ʉ̈u pãar thum agdaujö chikham kha khõsi wënʉrraajem chadcha; magʉm ãba mamʉ marau waragta jũrr agdaujö dich khapeen daupii abat anʉm.  
\v 11 Khõinaa wënʉrrajuuta ẽkhanaa nem inagdam wauju aai nʉm khai, ag gaaipaita nʉisit. Pãach juadamaucha phidkhabat, nawe maachdëu pãachig jaaujemjö.  
\v 12 Maagwai bithurgam khʉʉn Ẽwandam iek ʉ̈khaba nʉm khʉʉnaujã pãach mag oowai, pãar ëugar khaigba iekhabaju; mag nʉm dʉ̈i ĩchab pãach mag phidkhaawai pãachdëu nem ig nʉm atheejã pãar augchëbaju. 
\s1 Maach Pör Jesucristo bëeju Pabloou jaautarr 
\p  
\v 13 Khodamnaan, sĩi Ẽwandam iek ʉ̈khaba aajem khʉʉnjö pãach ökhĩirjuu apimaaugau, marau pãrag jaaum ig nʉm, jãga aajẽ mʉg maach Ẽwandam iek ʉ̈kha nʉm khʉʉn meewai.  
\v 14 Maadëu khaphʉ nʉm Jesús meewia deeu iiu phiidʉtarr. Magtarr aawai thãraucha i iek ʉ̈kha nʉm ötarr khʉʉnjã deeu ich Ẽwandamau phiriutkha auwia ich Jesús pierrum dʉ̈i bëejujã chadcha khaphʉ aju aai nʉm. 
\p  
\v 15 Magua maach Pör Jesús iekta maach iek gaai thʉwi pãrag khap amkhĩir marau mag nʉm: Maach Pör Jesús bëem ed maach agtha chi iiu durrum khʉʉn chan maach na khëchtarr khʉʉn na i khĩirphee pos aimabaju, maach nawe khëchtarr khʉʉnta nacha phiidʉtkhaju aawai.  
\v 16 Maach Pör Jesús ich bëem edan ichta nem iek theeg bëeju, Ẽwandam trompeta tẽe abarm dʉ̈i Arcangelau i pierrum jaauwai äa abarm ee. Mag ʉ̈gtharmua pierrwai Cristo iek ʉ̈kha nʉm meetarr khʉʉnta nacha iiu phiidʉtkhaju;  
\v 17 maimuata maach agtha chi iiu durrum khʉʉn sĩi ʉ̈gthaa edjã baug ee dëgölp jiirkha athamjö awi mag chi maach nawe meetarr khʉʉnpa ich mag i dʉ̈i ãba nʉisiju.  
\v 18 Mag i dʉ̈i ãba naaimaju aawai magʉm iek ig iyʉ̈ʉ nʉmuata warag agdaujö pãach khapeen khĩir onee apibat. 
\c 5  
\p  
\v 1 Khodamnaan, mamʉ jãagwaita mag maach phë awaan bëeju ed chan mua pãrag jaaupʉ̈ibam.  
\v 2 Ya pãrau khaphʉ nʉm, maach Pör Jesús bëem edan, sĩi nem jĩgkhaajemta edaar dëgölp nem jĩgkhabaichëmjöta barchëju.  
\v 3 Maguata chi ʉ̈khaba nʉm khʉʉnau, “Ĩsin chad maach khajapha khõinaa aphöbaadëbma” anʉm ee, dëgölp am öju ed barchëju, sĩi khajap chaai awaag dëgölp ʉʉi chaai machkhabaadëmjö. Magbarm ed chi thʉbagkha nʉisim khʉʉn chan ni ãbjã Ẽwandam jua eemua peerdʉbam.  
\v 4 Khodamnaan, pari pãar agtha warramjö sĩi khĩchag eeta khaba nʉm, mag maach Pör bëem edjã okhoppha nʉm oocheeg.  
\v 5 Ya pãran thumwe ararag eem khʉʉnau; ya pãar ãsdawam khʉʉnkha thʉnaabahab. Maach chan edaram khʉʉn khaba ni khĩchag eem khʉʉnjã khabam.  
\v 6 Magua warm khʉʉnjö sĩi parhooba dichdëu nem waumpierr wau wënʉrraju khaba nʉm; magju khãai wajaphata khĩir khaug naaju aai nʉm i bëewaim athee, sĩi pör ee nag wai nʉmjö okhopha khaba.  
\v 7 Maadëu khaphʉ nʉm, õran edaar paawaita khãidʉtkhaajem, maimua khëumamuata dötarr khai, edaar paawaita ĩchab khëch thʉnaajem.  
\v 8 Pari maachin ãsdawam khʉʉn aawai donnaanjö parhoob nem wauju khaba nʉm. Maachin Ẽwandam iek maachdëu ogdʉba ʉ̈kha nʉmta warag khõsi ʉ̈khanaa, Jesucristoou maach peerdʉ awaan bëejuuta ich mag khĩir eyaa wai wënʉrraju aai nʉm.  
\v 9 Ẽwandamau maach jʉr aauwai chan deeu ãsie maach gaai jua khʉaba ichdëu ampierr aagta maach jʉr aubajim. Irua maach jʉr autarran, maach Pör Jesucristo gaaimua ʉ̈u peerdʉ wënʉrramkhĩirta maach jʉr aujim.  
\v 10 Ichta maach kõit ʉdʉraa ich thõopijim, magbarm gaaimua deeu ich bëewai agtha iiu durrum oobaicheewai, wa meewi naawia khãijã, ĩchab ich dʉ̈i wënʉrramkhĩir ich dʉ̈i arraag.  
\v 11 Mag i dʉ̈i ãba naaimaju aawai ich jãg pãach nʉmjö pãach khapeen khĩir onee apinaa Ẽwandam iek jaau nʉmuajã agdaujö chikham ubʉ apijuuta ẽkhabat. 
\p  
\v 12 Khodamnaan, marau pãrag jaaum ig nʉmʉn ĩchab, ar pãach ee chi pörnaan Ẽwandam iek jaaunaa pãach wawiejem khʉʉn chan oob pãrau sĩi amag oobamjö amiet anʉmʉu, amag phagmaaugau.  
\v 13 Magʉm gaai phidkha durrum paar wajapha am daupiinaa am kha khõsi abat. Magnaa pãach wir aigpaijã khõinaa naajeet. 
\p  
\v 14 Khodamnaan, ar jãg phidkhamapha sĩsidʉm khʉʉnagjã ikhʉaba meeurrau sĩubat phidkhamkhĩir. Kha oneg chukhu nʉm khʉʉnjã khĩir onee apinaa bʉ̈ʉr abarm gaaimua pekau ee burrjöjöo nʉm khʉʉn juagjã oobat. Pari mag nem jaauwaijã khajapha ithũu abat am dʉ̈i. 
\p  
\v 15 Chikhamnau pãach dʉ̈i khaigba aawai oob ich agjö aju awia am dʉ̈i khaigba amiet. Magju khãai pãach nem waaupierr nem wajapha waujuuta ẽkhabat, pãach wir aigpai maimua thumaam khʉʉn dʉ̈i awiajã ich agjö. 
\p  
\v 16 Ed ëepierr ich mag onee abat.  
\v 17 Ed ëepierr Ẽwandamagta jëeub khaba jëeubat.  
\v 18 Mag jëeu nʉmua nem thumaam paar irig ʉ̈u ajim abat. Pãar Jesucristo dënkha naawai magta irua apim khõsi sim pãrag ich dʉ̈i. 
\p  
\v 19 Ẽwandam Akharau pãach khapeenag nem waupiewai idëu waupibat, oob magʉm waumiet aba.  
\v 20 Ẽwandamau khĩirjug deewia pãach ee i iek jaau nʉm khʉʉnau nem jaauwai, oob sĩi ũrbamjöo amiet.  
\v 21 Amau jaau nʉm thum wajapha ũrnaa chi wajaphampai pör ee athat.  
\v 22 Nem wau nʉmua maach pekau paarpapiejem nem warre thum isegbapʉ̈it. 
\p  
\v 23 Ẽwandam ichdëu õor khõinaa apiejemuata pãar wajapha pekau chukhu wai sĩekhiin ʉ̈u akham. Magua pãar kõit Ẽwandamag jëeu chirʉm, pãar akhaar, pãar mor maach chi ʉ̈rʉm cha maach iyʉ̈ʉ nʉmpa thumaa wajapha thʉnʉmta maach Pör Jesucristoou ich bëewai oochëmkhĩir.  
\v 24 Ich chi pãar jʉr autarrau chan ich iekhabarm bʉ̈ʉrjã sëukhaba sĩerrʉm. Í mag sĩerraawai ichdëu mag abarmjã chadcha sĩerrʉm. 
\s1 Pablo salud ãbmiecharam 
\p  
\v 25 Khodamnaan, maar kõitjã ĩchab Ẽwandamag jëeubat.  
\v 26 Maach khodnaan thumaam khʉʉnag mʉ salud deebat.  
\v 27 Maach Pör Jesuu mʉrʉg jaaupi sĩewai i iekta mua mʉch iek gaai thʉwi ẽsap gaai mʉg phã deepʉ̈i chirʉm. Mʉg mua phã deepʉ̈i chirʉm Ẽwandam gaaimua thum maach khodkha nʉm khʉʉn jʉ̈gdaar thʉ̈rbat, amach jʉ̈gʉucha ũrmkhĩir. 
\p  
\v 28 Maach Pör Jesucristoogta pãar kõit jëeu chiraajem, ichdëuta pãrau nemdam ig nʉm thumaa dedee amkhĩir. 
\p Mʉgdampai ajim pãrag jaaupʉ̈im ig chirarr. Ayoo keena, 
\cls Pablo